Second Department,

January, 1958 *

(January 27, 1958) In the Matter of the Application of Lawrence R. Knobel, for Admission to the Bar.

Motion to vacate order dated April 27, 1953, denying application for admission to the Bar, and for other relief, denied. Present — Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Beldock, Murphy and Ughetta, JJ.
